Dialogue Current Updates:
    Able to talk and continue talking with the 'e' button.
    Able to end conversation with the 'q' button.
    Able to end conversation by walking away.
        May be removed later if we want the character to be incapable of movement when in a dialogue box.
    Able to end the conversation by clicking the end conversation button.
    Able to continue the conversation by clicking the continue conversation button.
